<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/19263865-abigail">Abigail</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Yes, the book has three points of view: Marguerite Westing, Trip Andrews, and Rodger Gordon. 
</span>
